# Tasks — Example
# This is an example file. Copy to memory/tasks.md and fill in your details.
# CONSTITUTION §8: The live file is gitignored. Only this .example is committed.
# Updated by daily-planner.md, 11_session-closer.md, 12_daily-standup.md.

---

## Active Tasks

> Tasks currently in progress or queued. Updated after every session.
> Each task must be specific (not "work on thesis") and time-boxed.

| # | Task | Stage | Est. Hours | Status | Due | Blocker |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | [specific task] | Stage N | 2 | todo / in-progress / done / blocked | YYYY-MM-DD | — |
| 2 | [specific task] | Stage N | 1.5 | todo | YYYY-MM-DD | — |
| 3 | [specific task] | Stage N | 3 | blocked | YYYY-MM-DD | [blocker description] |

Status options: todo | in-progress | done | blocked | deferred

---

## Milestone Countdown Tasks

> Tasks tied to an upcoming milestone. Automatically elevated if milestone is within 14 days.

| Milestone | Due Date | Prep Task | Est. Hours | Status |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| [milestone name] | YYYY-MM-DD | [specific prep action] | N | todo |

---

## Weekly Plan

> Set by 12_daily-standup.md or daily-planner.md.

Week of: YYYY-MM-DD

| Day | Focus Area | Task | Time Block | Done? |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Monday | Research / Writing / Admin | [specific task] | N hrs | □ |
| Tuesday | ... | ... | ... | □ |
| Wednesday | ... | ... | ... | □ |
| Thursday | ... | ... | ... | □ |
| Friday | Admin / Reading | [lighter task] | N hrs | □ |

