## Resolved Blockers Log

> Appended by 13_stuck-triage.md. Personal problem-solving record.

| Date | Type | Description | Resolution | Time Lost |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| YYYY-MM-DD | technical | [brief description] | [what worked] | [hours] |

